Class PDDLAction.Effect

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.PDDLAction.Effect
  • Enclosing class:
    PDDLAction

    public class PDDLAction.Effect
extends java.lang.Object
    Class that represents an effect of a PDDL action. An effect is consists of an instantiated effect predicate and a list of conditions that must be met for the effect to take place.
